title: #92Noon Nordo in for PA!  Johnson/Grimm/Gleeman
description: Nordo is in for a special New Years Eve edition of 9 to Noon!  Ron Johnson joins the show for some in-depth Gophers and Vikings discussion.  Mike Grimm calls in to chat about the Outback Bowl.  Aaron Gleeman stops by the studio for some Twins offseason talk. In the middle of it all, Nordo takes us back to reflect on the 2019 Minnesota Vikings season.
